name: Briefing-segment-skipper
tagline: Use some javascript mp3 players to skip around audio and highlight sections
body:
## Audio Section Skipper
This was originally developed as a prototype for a new version of Dr. R. Albert Mohler's [_The Briefing_](http://www.albertmohler.com/category/the-briefing/) podcast.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
